subject: Dear Sir,
body:
Dear Sir,
We the Ocean Consultant are interested in investing in your country. Kindly confirm your private email address to our financial director Mr. Anton Kaltofen through his private email address,

subject: Re: Dear Sir,
body:
Hello Mr. Jeomg Changmin,
Thank you for reaching out. Could you please provide more information about the investment opportunity you are interested in pursuing in our country? I would like to learn more before sharing any contact details.
Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Larry
